librairie SDIF avec 2 utilitaires, tosdif, sdiftotext
-----------------------------------------------------


Makefile		Makefile general: all, clean, install, uninstall
Makefile.preamble	variables generales aux makefiles. INSTALL_ROOT
			permet de controler le lieu d'installation de
			la librairie.
Makefile.postamble	regles communes aux makefiles.




doc/		documentations de la librairie en html: index.html
sdif/		SOURCES de la librairie + fichiers des types predefinis.
others/		autres sources non incluses dans la librairie (obsolettes
		mais pourraient redevenir importantes)
obj/		.o repartis par machine
libsdif/	libsdif.a repartis par machine
tosdif/		utilitaire de conversion d'un fichier sdif text en fichier binaire
sdiftotext/	inverse de tosdif
files/		fichier tests. seul files/txt n'est pas vide au cvs checkout
test/		pour tester des fonctions particulieres
CVS/		gestion CVS




Memory Report
-------------

Object : Trying to find memory leak.

5 tokens can be added with -D (or /D windows) to have a memory report
of the allocations made with SdifMalloc, SdifCalloc and SdifRealloc.
If memory heap is not free with SdifFree, then this heap is taken as memory leak.

The 5 tokens are :
_SdifMemoryReport         to have a memory report at the end of execution (with the other token too).
_SdifMemoryReportAlloc    to have a report only about allocation and re-allocation
_SdifMemoryReportReAlloc  to have a report only about re-allocation
_SdifMemoryReportFree	    to have a report only about memory released to the system
_SdifMemoryBigReport		  to have a full report

If one of tokens _SdifMemoryReportAlloc, _SdifMemoryReportReAlloc, _SdifMemoryReportFree, _SdifMemoryBigReport
are defined, then _SdifMemoryReport is automaticaly defined.

All SdifFree must be before SdifGenKill which call SdifMrDrainBlockList.
SdifMrDrainBlockList is the function wich print the final memory report and drain the list of memory leak.

use memory report with another memory leak viewer (like Purify product) might give a bad idea of the memory free.
Don't distribute a programme linked with activated memory report, because it's more long.

